title: JetTabs 1.1.3 - Tabs and Accordions for Elementor Page Builder
description: Visit us on: https://www.nulledforums.org JetTabs WordPress Plugin is an efficient addon allowing to add stylish tabs and accordion blocks to the webpages and enrich them with all kinds of content, which can be built using Elementor widgets. The plugin is easy to use and customize, has multiple style settings. Explore the new horizons of building content with JetTabs plugin. This powerful addon for Elementor live page builder is cut for creating tabs, accordion blocks and even image accordions with vertical and horizontal layouts. JetTabs WordPress Plugin Features WORKS WITH ELEMENTOR CLASSIC ACCORDION IMAGE ACCORDION VERTICAL & HORIZONTAL LAYOUTS RICH IN STYLE SETTINGS FLAWLESS DESIGN FULLY RESPONSIVE
